snippet.title: Monsters University:Hide and Sneak
snippet.description: Even monsters have to go to school! And so does the crew from Disney’s® Monsters University. Help Mike practice for the Scare Games competition by navigating the obstacle course set in the Oozma Kappa frat house and scoring a perfect scare! A Disney® game.
